      "line": 28,
      "message": "Yes. There is a problem with the dns settings disappearing in ubuntu. After installing docker, the record will disappear from /etc/resolv.conf file. In this role I adding same record again. Adding record to file using host variable: \"{{ hostvars[groups.infrastructure[0]].cluster_ip }}\". This happening only in Debian.yml playbook. So in Rhel molecule test isn't necessary to have this variable.",
